  </para>
</problem>

<solution id="eip-838">
  <para id="eip-263">
 The medicine needs to be administered four times a day, during wake times.
  </para>
</solution>
</exercise><exercise id="eip-71"><problem id="eip-561">
  <para id="eip-566">
    gtt
  </para>
</problem>


</exercise><exercise id="eip-469"><problem id="eip-768">
  <para id="eip-331">
 I.V.
  </para>
</problem>

<solution id="eip-791">
  <para id="eip-565">
The medicine is to be administered intravenously.
  </para>
</solution>
</exercise><para id="eip-672">For the following exercises, convert between AM/PM time and time using the 24-hour clock.</para><exercise id="eip-293"><problem id="eip-993">
